title: Football Player of the Week: East Noble's Andrew McCormick
text:
Football Player of the Week: East Noble's Andrew McCormick 
By Kayla Crandall -21Alive October 22, 2015 Updated Oct 22, 2015 at 7:08 PM EDT 
NOBLE COUNTY, Ind. (21Alive) -- Due to Boy's High School Media Day on Wednesday, the 21Alive Parkview Sports Medicine Football Player of the Ween announcement had to be moved to Thursday. 
This week's winner is a young pup, East Noble Sophomore quarterback Andrew McCormick, who threw for 167 yards and 4 TD's in the Knights' 28-7 win over Bellmont last Friday. 
He added 71 on the ground, but you won't catch Andrew taking any of the credit for the great night.
